  <name>Truckers Tool Linux</name>
  <summary>Unofficial telemetry and profile manager for Euro Truck Simulator 2 on Linux</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Truckers Tool Linux is a native, modern, and open-source companion application designed for Euro Truck Simulator 2 (ETS2) and American Truck Simulator (ATS) on Linux.</p>
    <p>Features include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Save Profile Editing: Easily modify player properties such as Bank Money and Experience Points.</li>
      <li>Automatic backups before modifications (Restore point management).</li>
      <li>Native Linux interface using modern web technologies (Next.js and Electron).</li>
      <li>Easy to navigate dashboard for active game monitoring.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
